item.title: Aboutme
item.description:
Nice to meet you ! I am a Computer Science student with an interest in cybersecurity, Especially low-level security , i have practical knowledge in reverse-engineering, debuggers, vulnerabilities, and malware.

This is my personal blog where i will upload ctf solutions and other things that pique my interest.

Hope you have a great time - rtg.
